MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

91-1259. Forbes v. Midwest Air Charter, Inc.

Cuyahoga App. No. 56815. This cause is pending before the court as a discretionary appeal and cross-appeal from the Court of Appeals for Cuyahoga County. Upon consideration of the application of appellee/cross-appellant, Piper Aircraft Corporation, for dismissal of the cross-appeal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that said application be, and the same is hereby, granted, and the cross-appeal is dismissed.

IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that the appeal of Ina Forbes remain pending.
